<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 16:09:25 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列正统派极端分子在招募中心的战斗中失败，但他们正在赢得战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/haredi-extremists-lost-the-battle-at-the-recruitment-center-but-theyre-winning-the-war/00000191-2837-d5e8-a397-feff9d4e0000</link><description>通过资金充足、复杂且有时甚至是暴力的运动，强硬的正统派活动人士成功地减缓了将该社区融入以色列军队的努力。克服它们需要新的决心</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 15:58:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/haredi-extremists-lost-the-battle-at-the-recruitment-center-but-theyre-winning-the-war/00000191-2837-d5e8-a397-feff9d4e0000</guid></item><item><title>真主党向以色列北部开火，造成 19 人受伤，其中一人重伤；以色列国防军：拦截弹可能击中平民</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/19-wounded-by-hezbollah-fire-to-israels-north-idf-interceptor-may-have-hit-civilians/00000191-2812-dcd6-abf7-7e170da60000</link><description>军方正在调查为何拦截弹是从黎巴嫩发射的火箭发射的，但在未击中目标后未能在空中爆炸。周二早些时候，真主党附属组织 Al-Hadath 报道称，以色列国防军无人机袭击造成黎巴嫩南部 5 人死亡</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 15:45:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/19-wounded-by-hezbollah-fire-to-israels-north-idf-interceptor-may-have-hit-civilians/00000191-2812-dcd6-abf7-7e170da60000</guid></item><item><title>极右翼以色列说唱歌手分享未向媒体公开的警察录像</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israeli-rapper-shares-police-footage-not-released-to-the-media/00000191-27ab-ddbb-a7fd-affbf8a10000</link><description>视频显示，警察从海法的反战抗议者手中扯下巴勒斯坦旗帜。 《国土报》的镜头显示一名警察摄影师拍摄了后来在说唱歌手的 Telegram 频道上分享的内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 15:14:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israeli-rapper-shares-police-footage-not-released-to-the-media/00000191-27ab-ddbb-a7fd-affbf8a10000</guid></item><item><title>在伊朗请求军事援助后，普京要求伊朗避免以色列平民伤亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-08-06/ty-article/putin-asks-iran-to-avoid-israeli-civilian-casualties-after-iran-requests-military-aid/00000191-27f3-dbbc-ab95-37f371760000</link><description>一个俄罗斯代表团前往德黑兰，试图说服伊朗不要在对以色列的报复中针对平民，以防止大规模战争。 《纽约时报》报道称，伊朗要求提供先进的防空系统，消息人士称俄罗斯正在交付这些系统</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 14:45:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-08-06/ty-article/putin-asks-iran-to-avoid-israeli-civilian-casualties-after-iran-requests-military-aid/00000191-27f3-dbbc-ab95-37f371760000</guid></item><item><title>“黑色星期一”之后：华尔街的问题可能已经结束，但以色列的问题还没有结束</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/after-black-monday-wall-streets-problems-may-be-over-but-israels-arent/00000191-27cc-dcd6-abf7-77cf94f20000</link><description>周一，世界股市对经济衰退的担忧反应过度。但全球科技正面临人工智能的后遗症，这对以色列来说是个坏消息</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 13:18:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/after-black-monday-wall-streets-problems-may-be-over-but-israels-arent/00000191-27cc-dcd6-abf7-77cf94f20000</guid></item><item><title>“我们在等待死亡”：以色列贝都因人仍然无法抵御伊朗无人机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/waiting-for-death-israels-bedouins-still-have-no-protection-against-irans-drones/00000191-2750-dcd6-abf7-77574c9a0000</link><description>四月份受重伤的小女孩阿米娜·哈苏尼 (Amina al-Hassouni) 的家人在其中一处干河中过夜。在 Bir Hadaj 村，学校内的临时公共避难所无法容纳所有居民。伊朗无人机袭击四个月后，以色列内盖夫的贝都因社区仍然没有保护</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 12:56:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/waiting-for-death-israels-bedouins-still-have-no-protection-against-irans-drones/00000191-2750-dcd6-abf7-77574c9a0000</guid></item><item><title>市警察局长被指控袭击反内塔尼亚胡示威者、滥用权力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/city-police-chief-accused-of-assaulting-anti-netanyahu-demonstrators-abusing-power/00000191-274f-d642-a9d5-b74f78a40000</link><description>哈德拉警察局指挥官、总警司阿米特·波拉克 (Amit Pollak) 在逮捕退伍军人并没收他们搭建的设施后，涉嫌袭击、滥用职权和妨碍司法公正</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 12:30:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/city-police-chief-accused-of-assaulting-anti-netanyahu-demonstrators-abusing-power/00000191-274f-d642-a9d5-b74f78a40000</guid></item><item><title>包括青少年在内的十二名巴勒斯坦人在以色列对约旦河西岸的空袭和袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/eight-palestinians-including-teenagers-killed-in-israeli-airstrike-raid-in-west-bank/00000191-26f6-debd-a3df-e6ffbb7d0000</link><description>以色列对杰宁市的空袭造成四人死亡；另有四人在阿卡巴村被杀。巴勒斯坦卫生部称，自10月7日以来，以色列在约旦河西岸的炮火已造成600多名巴勒斯坦人死亡</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 11:49:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/eight-palestinians-including-teenagers-killed-in-israeli-airstrike-raid-in-west-bank/00000191-26f6-debd-a3df-e6ffbb7d0000</guid></item><item><title>因虐待而请愿关闭斯德泰曼中心后，以色列将在斯德泰曼中心开设两个新翼楼</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-open-two-new-wings-at-sde-teiman-after-petition-to-shut-center-down-over-abuse/00000191-26c3-d60f-a3d3-eec76b7d0000</link><description>上个月，在人权组织请愿关闭该拘留中心后，高等法院命令该州解释为什么该拘留中心没有依法运作。作为回应，国家宣布了改善拘留条件的新措施</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 11:41:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-open-two-new-wings-at-sde-teiman-after-petition-to-shut-center-down-over-abuse/00000191-26c3-d60f-a3d3-eec76b7d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列关于战争的两本新书：一本提出永恒的战争，另一本呼吁和平。两者都有缺陷</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/books/2024-08-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/two-flawed-israeli-books-on-the-war-one-offers-eternal-warfare-the-other-calls-for-peace/00000191-26d1-dab7-a3d3-eff929a10000</link><description>阿里·沙维特在《生存战争》中寻求将以色列变成现代的斯巴达，而乌里·巴尔-约瑟夫在《铁墙之外》中主张外交安排。然而，两者都忽视了以色列在民族主义、宗教统治下的变化</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 11:27:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/books/2024-08-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/two-flawed-israeli-books-on-the-war-one-offers-eternal-warfare-the-other-calls-for-peace/00000191-26d1-dab7-a3d3-eff929a10000</guid></item><item><title>为帝国服务：古代耶路撒冷如何变得伟大</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-08-06/ty-article/in-the-service-of-empires-how-ancient-jerusalem-became-great/00000191-271a-d695-a1f9-b75b57e50000</link><description>著名圣经考古学家以色列芬克尔斯坦的新书得出结论，古代耶路撒冷和犹大在为外国帝国服务时最繁荣</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 10:38:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-08-06/ty-article/in-the-service-of-empires-how-ancient-jerusalem-became-great/00000191-271a-d695-a1f9-b75b57e50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队撤离在巴勒斯坦土地上非法设立的定居者前哨基地，担心西岸新战线</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-forces-evacuate-outpost-built-on-palestinian-land-fearing-a-new-west-bank-front/00000191-26c4-dc6a-a397-2fdd20a20000</link><description>《辛贝特》最近警告称，根据情报，来自吉夫阿特奥兹锡安前哨基地的恐怖行为可能会将约旦河西岸从战争的次要战线转变为主要战线</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 08:50:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-forces-evacuate-outpost-built-on-palestinian-land-fearing-a-new-west-bank-front/00000191-26c4-dc6a-a397-2fdd20a20000</guid></item><item><title>尽管埃尔多安发出威胁，美国仍指望土耳其进行调解以避免中东战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/despite-erdogans-threats-u-s-is-counting-on-turkish-mediation-to-avert-mideast-war/00000191-248e-d19b-a3b7-b6df3e220000</link><description>尽管埃尔多安最近威胁要入侵以色列，但埃尔多安在很大程度上参与了美国外交努力，以限制伊朗对伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚在其领土上被暗杀事件的愤怒反应</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 03:00:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/despite-erdogans-threats-u-s-is-counting-on-turkish-mediation-to-avert-mideast-war/00000191-248e-d19b-a3b7-b6df3e220000</guid></item><item><title>当纳斯鲁拉在演讲中吹嘘真主党无人机深入以色列时，以色列北部的火箭警报响起</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article-live/biden-harris-briefed-on-mideast-developments-palestinians-four-killed-in-west-bank-raid/00000191-2581-dcd6-abf7-778716870000</link><description>戈兰地区委员会：以色列北部居民必须留在避难所附近，并尽量减少不必要的旅行 ■ 哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部表示，自 10 月 7 日以来，至少有 39,653 名巴勒斯坦人在加沙丧生 ■ 真主党声称对以色列北部的无人机袭击负责 ■ 以色列国防军，辛贝特称以色列战斗机袭击了黎巴嫩南部真主党军事基地</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 02:37:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article-live/biden-harris-briefed-on-mideast-developments-palestinians-four-killed-in-west-bank-raid/00000191-2581-dcd6-abf7-778716870000</guid></item><item><title>联盟针锋相对地否决了赋予以色列发布限制令的广泛权力的法案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/coalition-tit-for-tat-nixes-bill-giving-israel-sweeping-powers-to-issue-restraining-orders/00000191-242b-d19b-a3b7-b67fc6400000</link><description>拟议的法律将赋予地方法院权力，禁止公民离开家、使用互联网或到以色列境外旅行</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 21:44:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/coalition-tit-for-tat-nixes-bill-giving-israel-sweeping-powers-to-issue-restraining-orders/00000191-242b-d19b-a3b7-b67fc6400000</guid></item><item><title>真主党对以色列的威胁目前超过了伊朗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/.premium/hezbollahs-threat-on-israel-currently-outweighs-irans/00000191-2405-dc0c-a395-ae376d8d0000</link><description>来自黎巴嫩的袭击可能会以前所未有的强度针对以色列北部和中部的军事和战略地点。以色列需要根据火灾规模和各条战线造成的损失来调整其反应</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 20:22:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/.premium/hezbollahs-threat-on-israel-currently-outweighs-irans/00000191-2405-dc0c-a395-ae376d8d0000</guid></item><item><title>数十名巴勒斯坦囚犯的证词描述了加沙战争期间以色列监狱的条件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/.premium/dozens-of-testimonies-from-palestinians-describe-israeli-jails-conditions-during-gaza-war/00000191-238f-d825-abd9-afaf1a3b0000</link><description>以色列-巴勒斯坦非政府组织 B&amp;#39;Tselem 的一份新报告披露了自加沙战争开始以来被以色列拘留的数十名巴勒斯坦人的证词。大多数人未经起诉就被释放，他们的叙述详细描述了日常虐待、饥饿、羞辱、剥夺睡眠和拒绝医疗的情况</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 19:18:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/.premium/dozens-of-testimonies-from-palestinians-describe-israeli-jails-conditions-during-gaza-war/00000191-238f-d825-abd9-afaf1a3b0000</guid></item><item><title>当以色列准备进行报复时，伊朗到底发生了什么？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-08-05/ty-article-podcast/what-is-really-going-on-in-iran-while-israel-braces-for-retaliation/00000191-2363-d522-a9df-7f6be5e00000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 19:16:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-08-05/ty-article-podcast/what-is-really-going-on-in-iran-while-israel-braces-for-retaliation/00000191-2363-d522-a9df-7f6be5e00000</guid></item><item><title>调查发现九名工作人员可能参与了 10 月 7 日对以色列的袭击，联合国解雇了他们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/un-fires-9-staffers-after-probe-finds-possible-involvement-in-oct-7-attack-on-israel/00000191-23c1-dcd6-abf7-77c727160000</link><description>联合国秘书长办公室在一份简短声明中宣布了这一举措，但没有详细说明近东救济工程处工作人员在袭击中可能扮演的角色；联合国监督机构表示，这一决定是根据以色列在与以色列当局的讨论中提供的证据做出的</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 18:26:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/un-fires-9-staffers-after-probe-finds-possible-involvement-in-oct-7-attack-on-israel/00000191-23c1-dcd6-abf7-77c727160000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 304 天：10 月 7 日，九名近东救济工程处工作人员因可能参与其中而被解雇</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-304-nine-unrwa-workers-fired-for-possible-involvement-in-october-7/00000191-234a-dcd6-abf7-774f440f0001</link><description>西方高级外交官估计，伊朗将在 24 至 48 小时内对哈尼亚在德黑兰的事件做出回应 ■ 伊朗表示无意升级地区紧张局势，但认为需要惩罚以色列 ■ 俄罗斯安全会议秘书正在德黑兰与伊朗领导人会面 ■土耳其表示打算在国际法院正式加入南非针对以色列的种族灭绝案 ■ 这是战争开始 304 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 16:53:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-304-nine-unrwa-workers-fired-for-possible-involvement-in-october-7/00000191-234a-dcd6-abf7-774f440f0001</guid></item></channel></rss>